Description

  Offers various utilities for various tasks.

  * Arrays

  Convert arrays to list;

  * Charset

  Serializable character set class;

  * {{{./format.html}Format}}

  Format and parsers for byte unit, color, date duration, enums, Internet
socket address, local and graphics point;

  * Mnemonic

  Accelerator and mnemonic classes;

  * {{{./posixlocale.html}POSIX Locale}}

  Locale as used in POSIX platforms. Contains the language, country and
character set.

  * Properties

  List property change event and support;

  * Resources

  Converter utilities for URI and URL;

  * Strings

  Map to table string, to underscore converter;

  * System

  System selector;

  * Textmatch

  Search and replaces tokens of texts, is used to set configurations in
text configuration files;

  * Textposition

  Text and icon positions for tool bars and buttons;

  * Version

  Comparable version number. Compares the major, minor and revision version
numbers.

